hpc_dataR Documentation

High-performance computing system data

Description

Kuhn and Johnson (2013) describe a data set where characteristics of unix jobs were used to classify there completion times as either very fast (1 min or less, VF), fast (150 min, F), moderate (530 min, M), or long (greater than 30 min, L).

Value

hpc_data

a tibble

Source

Kuhn, M., Johnson, K. (2013) Applied Predictive Modeling, Springer.

Examples


data(hpc_data)
str(hpc_data)
